review: Dental implants replaces the missing teeth. People usually think Dental implants will be painful. But it is a very simple procedure and no pain. It usually take 3 to 4 month to complete whole process. Ir requires 3 to 4 visits. At the first visit doctor will examine the position of missing teeth.CD scan may be required in some cases to verify bone position. Then implant will be placed in the missing teeth place after giving external anesthesia. the procedure is totally painless. After fixing the implant, it requires 12 weeks to arrange a cap on top of the implant.

Visited Venu's dental clinic in Madhapur for my dental checkup, he clearly explained the issues with my wisdom tooth and recommended to have them removed. the office staff do frequent followup calls to check on the healing process.

review: My wife R Venkata Laxmi suffering with severe teeth pain.  Before going to Venu dental clinic I took her to nearest dental clinic at Gayatri hills. The doctor examined and said she needs root canal treatment and caps to be fixed. I agree for that and paid money in advance. They called continuesly for one week for treatment, they completed treatment but day by day pain is increasing. She very much distrubed physically and mentally with her treatment. Immediately I went to Venu dental hospital at Madhapur. Dr Venugopal sir examined her and given treatment. Within one week it was cured and she is happy. I am very much happy with his treatment and highly satisfied. Also very happy with his staff cooperation and good follow up. I am happily recomend to my friends, relatives and my colleagues to Venu dental hospital.

They gave me local anaesthesia so that I don't feel pain.
